        "category": "ancestry",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You've trained your tail to move with incredible precision, practicing a specific set of underhanded skills until they become second nature. When you attempt to [[/act disable-device]] or [[/act pick-a-lock]], if you're holding no items other than tools to help you Disable a Device or Pick a Lock, you can spend an additional action to use your tail to help with the attempt. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to your check to Disable a Device or Pick a Lock. On a success or critical success, you achieve an additional success if the device or lock requires more than one success.</p>"
        },
